output.analysis:
Let me analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: No CMF number is present, but this isn't conclusive by itself.
2. Candidate Reference: The post directly references George Simion, who is a confirmed presidential candidate (Position 2 on the official list).
3. Wide Population Targeting: - This is a paid advertisement on Facebook and Instagram - Targets a large audience (500,001-1,000,000 potential reach) - Uses multiple hashtags to increase visibility - Announces a public march in Suceava
4. Electoral Objective: - Uses hashtag #georgesimionpresedinte - Organizes a "March of Support for George Simion" - Uses campaign-related hashtags like #alegeri2024 - Clear intention to rally support for a presidential candidate
5. Journalism: This is not journalistic content - it's an announcement for a campaign event.
6. Personal Opinion: This is not a personal opinion but rather an organized campaign activity announcement.
The post clearly constitutes electoral propaganda as it meets all criteria under Article 36(7): a) Directly references a candidate b) Used during campaign period c) Has clear electoral objective d) Is not journalistic content

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Directly promotes a presidential candidate - Organizes a support march specifically for electoral purposes - Uses electoral campaign hashtags - Is a paid advertisement targeting a large audience - Has clear electoral objective to gather support for the candidate
conclusion.message-for-police: SC VIDEO DANCRYS-STUDIO S.R.L, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui material de propaganda electorala pentru candidatul prezidential George Nicolae Simion dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie electorala (dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024). Postarea cu ID-ul 546433941508702 promoveaza un mars de sustinere pentru candidatul George Simion, utilizand hashtag-uri specifice campaniei prezidentiale (#georgesimionpresedinte, #alegeri2024), si are un obiectiv electoral clar de mobilizare si influentare a alegatorilor prin organizarea unui mars de sustinere. Materialul este distribuit ca reclama platita pe Facebook si Instagram, cu un reach estimat intre 500.001 si 1.000.000 de persoane, demonstrand intentia clara de a influenta comportamentul electoral al unui numar semnificativ de alegatori dupa incheierea perioadei legale de campanie.
